00:21:25.620 --> 00:21:28.880 align:middle line:90%
in annihilating the Earth.

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:31.520 align:middle line:84%
The extent of the
devaluing of life on Earth

00:21:31.520 --> 00:21:34.570 align:middle line:84%
has become so extreme
in recent years

00:21:34.570 --> 00:21:37.280 align:middle line:84%
that there have been
interventions made

00:21:37.280 --> 00:21:40.120 align:middle line:84%
