00:21:52.120 --> 00:21:55.290 align:middle line:84%
In harmony with the
wholeness of creation,

00:21:55.290 --> 00:21:58.820 align:middle line:90%
both invisible and manifest.

00:21:58.820 --> 00:22:03.550 align:middle line:84%
In the service all creative
effort, not destruction.

00:22:03.550 --> 00:22:07.070 align:middle line:84%
In loving regard
for all being, not

00:22:07.070 --> 00:22:12.680 align:middle line:84%
