There are many different kinds
of these encounter experiences.

00:23:22.710 --> 00:23:29.882 align:middle line:84%
And all I want to say is that
this is the way it came to me.

00:23:29.882 --> 00:23:31.590 align:middle line:84%
What happened in the
encounter experience

00:23:31.590 --> 00:23:34.940 align:middle line:84%
was that I was on a
meditation retreat

00:23:34.940 --> 00:23:37.630 align:middle line:84%
in the Southern California
desert participating

00:23:37.630 --> 00:23:42.490 align:middle line:84%
in the second part of an
ancient mystery school retreat.

00:23:42.490 --> 00:23:46.770 align:middle line:84%
So I think it's important
to acknowledge the context.

00:23:46.770 --> 00:23:48.870 align:middle line:84%
I'm not trying to say that
there's a cause effect

00:23:48.870 --> 00:23:49.990 align:middle line:90%
relation.

00:23:49.990 --> 00:23:53.230 align:middle line:84%
But I'm trying to say that
I was in a field phenomenon.

00:23:53.230 --> 00:23:59.110 align:middle line:84%
I had been doing meditation
on all the chakras

00:23:59.110 --> 00:24:03.545 align:middle line:84%
in a fairly intensive setting
with a group for 12 days.

00:24:03.545 --> 00:24:06.440 align:middle line:90%


00:24:06.440 --> 00:24:10.420 align:middle line:84%
We'd done many
ceremonies and rituals.

00:24:10.420 --> 00:24:14.310 align:middle line:84%
And the conference was over and
I was living on the East Coast

00:24:14.310 --> 00:24:19.130 align:middle line:84%
at that time and I was going
to fly back the next day.

00:24:19.130 --> 00:24:23.000 align:middle line:84%
And a friend and I said,
well, you know, why don't we

00:24:23.000 --> 00:24:28.280 align:middle line:84%
go up the mountain over Palm
Springs and look at the view

00:24:28.280 --> 00:24:29.880 align:middle line:90%
