00:24:29.880 --> 00:24:33.070 align:middle line:84%
And so the two of
us got in the car

00:24:33.070 --> 00:24:35.580 align:middle line:84%
and we started driving
up the mountain.

00:24:35.580 --> 00:24:37.650 align:middle line:84%
We'd had dinner
with a group of us.

00:24:37.650 --> 00:24:43.727 align:middle line:84%
And it was probably about
8:00 in the evening.

00:24:43.727 --> 00:24:44.560 align:middle line:90%
Something like that.

