It was still light
when we started anyway.

00:24:47.190 --> 00:24:49.420 align:middle line:84%
So we began to make
our way up one of them

00:24:49.420 --> 00:24:53.050 align:middle line:84%
beautiful mountains
surrounding Palm Springs.

00:24:53.050 --> 00:24:59.054 align:middle line:84%
And there were two features
about the actual journey

00:24:59.054 --> 00:24:59.720 align:middle line:90%
